PREAMBLE

This license applies to any program in the PHTV distribution that contains
a notice placed by the copyright holder saying it may be distributed under
the terms of this General Public License.

PHTV - Vietnamese Input Method for macOS
Project repository: https://github.com/PhamHungTien/PHTV
OpenKey repository: https://github.com/tuyenvm/OpenKey

================================================================================

This program is based on the original OpenKey engine for Vietnamese text input.
The engine components (Vietnamese.cpp, Engine.cpp, etc.) provide the core
functionality for handling Vietnamese typing with various input methods
(Telex, VNI, Simple Telex) and character encodings (Unicode, TCVN3, VNI).

