================================================================================

This project uses and adapts code and concepts from the OpenKey Vietnamese
input method engine developed by Tuyến Võ Minh. PHTV (Phạm Hùng Tiến Vietnamese)
extends this engine with modern macOS integration, SwiftUI interface, and additional
features while maintaining GPL-3.0 compliance.

OpenKey: https://github.com/tuyenvm/OpenKey

For more information about GPL-3.0, visit: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html
